ProjectTitle:
NottingHillCarnival2013

Package Name:
com.2013.NottingHillCarnival



INTRODUCTION:
-------------

A phone gap app that displays a map, the sound systems on the map , and uses gprs / 3g to show the user's location on the map.

It has these important features:

1. SLIDE PANEL LAYOUT

2. GPRS / 3G CALCULATE POSITION

3. FACEBOOK INTEGRATION - PUBLISH MY LOCATION

4. ADD ANALYTICS - FLURRY ( OR LOCALYTICS - FREE TRIAL? )

5. TWITTER IF AVAILABLE

6. PUSH NOTIFICATIONS 
	- REMEMBER TO UPDATE THE APP - SATURDAY
	- SPONSORS MESSAGE - ...
	- REMEMBER CARNIVAL ENDS AT ____
	- UPDATE LOCATIONS

7. LOCALLY STORED MAP IMAGE , AND LOCALLY STORED LATEST TWEET



